Larger zoom, right click with eraser to replace colors, a secret brush (not useful at all), and "draw opaque" for the selection tool. "Draw Opaque" isn't really hidden, but it's my favorite MS Paint feature.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3504">Kasumi</a> — Thu Feb 03, 2011 12:12 pm</p><hr />
